n希望可以開心番 但內心係軟弱 缺乏安全感 好想捉緊住對方 <br />\n但對方明顯冇左興趣同依賴 你越想捉緊 對方只會走得越遠 <br />\n你同佢分開左就比較難係返埋一齊 再繼續落去都只係換黎更多煩惱 困擾自己 當日分開左就無打算回頭 就算你咩都應承 去改變 但都只會對你唔公平<br />\n就咁睇牌復合機會不大 而且呢個人唔太適合你了"},{"pid":"f76e8eb3d832cd734ecb1504f70e3e37d1602060","tid":1011964,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b754733bae93cb8eec14cdc05c7c6046820eed","tid":1011964,"uid":14171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d62295685eae3f40c743ec53d72bd9001ddafc9","tid":1011964,"uid":35745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d460b9cceef4655445079721c0c499dd96717e","tid":1011964,"uid":127010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"1.Ria<br />\n2.女<br />\n3.C<br />\n唔該曬你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea81d45980113d6d91590361c0fa171ae3ab32f","tid":1011964,"uid":121203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"名： Ian<br />\n性別： 男<br />\nC"},{"pid":"0fa2e277e44b9ddc96fa7d6bb3465fbba1b3423c","tid":1011964,"uid":218519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"1.HC<br />\n2.女<br />\n3.B"},{"pid":"79a0802ee002d36b2a3bca59b8103b7556c2529b","tid":1011964,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:40:07.000Z","msg":"1. ben<br />\n2. 男<br />\n3. hehe 單身 a0 有冇機會拍拖"},{"pid":"e6f51b6213faf8114ccaedfa13b8d4d94d3377fa","tid":1011964,"uid":121203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ea81d45980113d6d91590361c0fa171ae3ab32f","tid":1011964,"uid":121203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019